metadata.name: MONSTER AMONG US
metadata.description:
"Monster Among Us"

Where two astronauts are very scared and threatened seeing a gigantic alien with deadly tentacles trying to eat them. And they are in helpless situation. Where they don't know what to do who to ask help for. If you were in that situation what would you have done?

It is also science fiction story where a dangerous creature or alien is present in outer space. It could also refer to a hypothetical scenario where a real-life organism or entity is discovered in space and is perceived as a monster or threat. 

In general, "monster in space" suggests a story or situation where a dangerous or unknown entity is present in the vast expanse of outer space.


So i tried to show it like a movie scene in very detailed way because i like to create my art in detail. 

This is high quality 2k 3D render in maya. MP4 Format
